    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the CFD model provides sufficient evidence to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device at MRL 2. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Overall assurance level declared Medium based on team judgment of the aggregate factor performance. The discretization error factor GCI values of 12–19% were considered acceptable by the team given qualitative flow topology agreement, and the decision was accepted without formal uncertainty quantification or third-level mesh refinement.",
